{"tid":16754,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求一隻舊game既名","createTime":"2016-12-01T14:45:43.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T03:42:48.000Z","uid":46498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4ee3ffb59ee83c7b8dfc3a81a1fbc321be538b7d","tid":16754,"uid":46498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T14:45:43.000Z","msg":"應該係SLG game黎， 主要靠招唤怪物黎戰鬥，<br />\n而招怪要用Mp,  mp主要靠怪物霸地圖上既魔法陣黎回復。<br />\n<br />\n怪物都幾多種類，印象較深既有吸血鬼，獨角獸同鱷魚(op) <br />\n<br />\n隻game細個玩既，果時英文廢唔係好明劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n主角係一個光頭仔鬼佬魔法師，大約係講佢唔知點解去左個異世界，仲同佢阿叔失散左，於是佢踏上千里尋叔之旅。<br />\n成隻game有3 章，第1章係搵阿叔，第2章 係同阿叔一齊集合圓桌武士預備打boss, 途中仲識到囡囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />...同死左阿叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />， 第3章 係打boss bbq ending, 而每過一章，主角都會急速老化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打有印象？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be778367f132701e82b8f7da4dccafc38a175dbc","tid":16754,"uid":46498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T14:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a50c53c392816b7d1124addd31f20bb778da5a50","tid":16754,"uid":46498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:42:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}